</ul>
<p>December 7, 1995<P><ul><LI><i>Progress on Point:</i>  <a href="/pff/pop-17.html">Key Issues Before the Telecom Conferees</a> by <a href="/pff/people/sfellow.html#Myers">William C. Myers</a></ul>

<P>December 4, 1995<P><ul><LI><i>Progress on Point:</i>  <a href="/pff/pop-15.html">Giving Thanks for Constructive Envy</a> by <a href="/pff/people/sfellow.html#Olasky">Marvin Olasky</a></ul>

