<input type="checkbox" name="for-small">"For Small Business, Less Government is Good Government," <i>The Washington Times</i>, December 8, 1994<p>
<input type="checkbox" name="economy-presidential">"The Economy's 'Presidential Lag,'" <I>The Journal of Commerce</i>, July 18, 1994<p>
