http://www.lead-inst.org:80/townhall/sotu96/sotu.html 204.71.237.80 19970210124943 text/html 41484
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Monday, 10-Feb-97 12:50:27 GMT
Last-modified: Wednesday, 24-Jan-96 14:00:26 GMT
