<TITLE>Joe Jacobs is the founder and chief executive officer of Jacobs Engineering Group Inc -- PFF</TITLE>


</HEAD>

<BODY bgcolor="#FFFFFF" background="/pff/notebook.gif" LINK="#8C1717" VLINK="#545454" ALINK="#FF0000"> <a href="/pff/"><img src="/pff/pffdoc.gif" border="0" align="right"></a>
<center>
<blockquote><ul>
<P>
<h2>Joe Jacobs</h2>

</center><P>

<B>Joe Jacobs</B> is the founder and chief executive officer of
Jacobs Engineering Group Inc.  He has contributed to numerous
charities and in 1987 established the Jacobs Family Foundation.
 The goal of the Foundation is to provide technical assistance
to organizations it funds and is attempting to devise a methodology
to measure the effectiveness of philanthropic dollars.


</ul><P>
