  <li> Took bribes from Tyson Foods Inc., which was under regulatory
  control  of his Agriculture Department.
<p>
  <FONT  COLOR=#FF0000>Espy has resigned and is under investigation by a Special Counsel</FONT>
<p></ol></ul>
