<p>
<li>Dick Armey, <I>The Freedom Revolution</I> (Washington D.C.: Regnery Publishing, Inc., 1995), p. 238.
<p>
    <li>James Bovard, "How Fair Are the Fair Labor Standards?"  <I>Regulation: The Cato Review of Business & Government</I>, Vol. 18, No. 1 (1995).
<p>
